Name: Vosaria: Lair of the Forgotten
About the game: A pump-action 2D side-scrolling game with different enemy types. along with a jump-to-the-roof mechanic that spices up the combat. Avoid traps, survive enemy encounters and upgrade your weapons and gear to overcome the challenges. - Multiple guns to unlock. - 10 x Health, armor and Ammo upgrades. - Alternative-fire upgrades for your weapons.
